## Code Owners

This file specifies who should review code changes.

```
# Security files
SECURITY.md @ManishPatil2005

# Core application
main.py @ManishPatil2005

# Templates and UI
templates/ @ManishPatil2005
static/ @ManishPatil2005

# Documentation
*.md @ManishPatil2005

# Configuration
requirements.txt @ManishPatil2005
Procfile @ManishPatil2005
render.yaml @ManishPatil2005
```

### Review Process

- Security changes: Require immediate review
- Core logic changes: Require review before merge
- Documentation: Can be merged after single review
- Tests: Must pass before merge

### Branch Protection

- `master` branch is protected
- Requires at least 1 approval
- Requires all checks to pass
- Requires updated branch before merge
